{"tid":1051456,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首咁耐以黎讀過最霸氣，最有境界嘅詩詞","createTime":"2019-03-07T15:22:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-27T12:22:33.000Z","uid":115169,"like":19,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f354f214d5852a21b673d4ecee6d9d574f8f79c3","tid":1051456,"uid":115169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"臨江仙 楊慎<br />\n滾滾長江東逝水，浪花淘盡英雄；<br />\n是非成敗轉頭空，青山依舊在、幾度夕陽紅。<br />\n白髮漁樵江渚上，慣看秋月春風；<br />\n一壺濁酒喜相逢，古今多少事、都付笑談中。<br />\n<br />\n  細個第一次睇三國演義聽過首主題曲，大左認真讀番，呢個其實先係做人最高境界- 睇透一切塵世間嘅功名俗利，泰山崩于前而色不变，心境平和更逍遙於俗世之外，一種難以形容的高尚情操。"},{"pid":"19d2896975f27d11d2983fcde3fe51260ff7c8ac","tid":1051456,"uid":228436,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:23:30.000Z","msg":"窗前明月光"},{"pid":"8e5b7d7fbbf620e0d7426087bd3af9407f455712","tid":1051456,"uid":228436,"like":29,"dislike":5,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:23:57.000Z","msg":"我現時自己肯做飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c3d3e3293d75c3346b1016ab7d73943966a7b0","tid":1051456,"uid":124491,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"大陸仔"},{"pid":"812d9a66db838ed6f904fbfa60d40ecef4895bae","tid":1051456,"uid":140580,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:24:27.000Z","msg":"莫聽穿林打葉聲，何妨吟嘯且徐行。竹杖芒鞋輕勝馬，誰怕？一蓑煙雨任平生。<br />\n料峭春風吹酒醒，微冷，山頭斜照卻相迎。回首向來蕭瑟處，歸去，也無風雨也無晴。"},{"pid":"b3e42372261fef1e1544a0572e03a86677e9de34","tid":1051456,"uid":228436,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"鵝鵝鵝 跟著唔知咩勃青波"},{"pid":"0450e18de959240712b0b03327bb26d40cb92046","tid":1051456,"uid":56088,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0